# рҹ“„ DocuMind AI

### *Ask your documents anything.*

DocuMind AI is a **multi-document AI-powered question answering system (RAG)** that allows users to upload documents and interact with them using natural language. It leverages **semantic search (FAISS)** and **local LLMs (Ollama)** to provide accurate, context-aware answers.

---

## рҹҡҖ Features

### рҹ“Ӯ Multi-Document Support

* Upload multiple PDF or TXT files
* Switch between documents seamlessly
* Independent processing for each document

### рҹ§  Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)

* Converts documents into embeddings
* Uses FAISS for fast semantic search
* Retrieves relevant context before generating answers

### рҹ’¬ Conversational Chat Interface

* Ask multiple questions per document
* Maintains conversation history
* Clean chat-style UI

### рҹӨ– AI-Powered Answers

* Uses local LLM (Ollama)
* Context-aware responses
* Avoids hallucination by restricting to document content

### рҹ’ҫ Persistent Chat History

* Saves chat per document
* Automatically loads previous conversations
* Enables session continuity

### вҡЎ Optimized Performance

* Efficient chunking strategy
* Context size control for faster responses
* Lightweight architecture

---

## рҹҸ—пёҸ Project Architecture

```text
Document вҶ’ Text Extraction вҶ’ Cleaning вҶ’ Chunking
        вҶ’ Embeddings вҶ’ FAISS Vector Store
        вҶ’ Query вҶ’ Context Retrieval вҶ’ LLM вҶ’ Answer
```

